<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Best Buy estimate lowered.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Best Buy estimate lowered.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- EVEREN Securities Inc Friday lowered its estimate for Best Buy Inc's third quarter earnings to $0.03 a share from $0.15.</p>
<p>-- It also reduced estimates for Best Buy's fiscal 1997 earnings to $0.45 from $0.70 and fiscal 1998 earnings to $0.70 from $0.83.</p>
<p>-- Best Buy shares lost 3/8 Friday to close at 12-7/8.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
